reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to install and lovely but wont last on a single charge
reviews.reviewText: This is my first time using it and it wokrs fine for the price. So bright and has different nice modes.An update: it doesn't charge really well. Lights stay for a couple of hours on each charge even though I had it under the sun charging for about six hours.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These were installed in a new barn for night lighting during evening feedings and kidding. The panels were easy to install on an exterior wall, the light hung nicely and quickly. They do not come on if there is light, even low light does not allow these to turn on. Once it's dark out...the lighting is really nice. Not too bright, adjustable light, timer and the goats do well with it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 7, 2024
reviews.reviewText: We are not impressed with the solar lights. Our first order did not work and we had to get a replacement.Now the 2nd order has quit after 2 months use. We feel the solar generator has failed on both sets.Would not recommend - not a quality item

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewText: I would always buy these when I need them they are the best ones I’ve seen yet bright & last a long time good price

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars I really like these lights
reviews.reviewText: I love how cute these string lights are. Set up is super easy. Stake the solar panel to the ground or attach it to something. Lights only last a few hours per night but it’s been cloudy out for most of the time I’ve had it. But I do love them and plan to order more!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Beautiful solar-powered string lights for my entry
reviews.reviewText: Installation was the hardest part. I carefully measured out and sank wire nails into my eve to hang the string. During the day, there was no way to gauge my success. The spot I picked for the solar panel was in partial shade. Will it be enough juice? It was! On the first two nights, I was surprised by blinking lights when night fell. But I programmed the remote to level them out. Now, every nightfall I get the beautiful entry you see in the picture. The bulbs may be plastic, but they look like glass. I am happy with these lights, though I wish there was more instruction included.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Very hard to get to work properly. See update.
reviews.reviewText: The lights are easy to hang and give off a bright light. However, the lights don’t work properly. I can’t get them to stay in a steady light mode. They just keep cycling through all of the modes. The lights also don’t work unless it is a pitch dark. I had to put a cover over the sensor to make the lights go on. I have other string lights on the sides of these lights and they work fine. I am returning these lights and will find another set.Update. I was able to get them working by adjusting the mode on the back of the solar charging panel. The remote doesn’t work ( at least not for me). So now the lights have gone on the past 4 nights and look good. We will see how they last. I would raise to 3 1/2 stars.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 21, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Great product for the price. Really happy with them

reviews.reviewTitle: Muy buenas pero no hay modo fijo, solo titilante.
reviews.reviewText: Son de muy buena calidad y las celdas solares/batería funcionan muy bien.Algo que no me gustó es que no puedo ponerlas en modo encendido fijo, tiene varios estilo pero en todas se prenden y apagan rítmicamente, por lo que para adornar un lugar es muy buena opción, pero para iluminar el espacio no es nada cómodo que estén prendiendo y apagando.

reviews.reviewTitle: Sólo funcionaron un par de días
reviews.reviewText: El panel solar dejó de cargar al segundo día y ya no encienden.
El panel solar dejó de funcionar :c
